IMAPAccount domain
Host imap.mailserver.com
Port 993
User user@domain.tld
PassCmd "cat /mnt/data/spamfilter/config/mbsync/mailpass"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore domain-remote
Account domain

MaildirStore domain-local
Path /mnt/data/spamfilter/mail/domain/
Inbox /mnt/data/spamfilter/mail/domain/INBOX

Channel domain-inbox
Far :domain-remote:INBOX
Near :domain-local:INBOX
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel domain-junk
Far :domain-remote:Junk
Near :domain-local:Junk
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group domain
Channel domain-inbox
Channel domain-junk
